Package org.apache.drill.exec.compile

Class CheckMethodVisitorFsm

java.lang.Object
org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
org.apache.drill.exec.compile.CheckMethodVisitorFsm
public class CheckMethodVisitorFsm extends org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
A MethodVisitor that verifies the required call sequence according to http://asm.ow2.org/asm50/javadoc/user/org/objectweb/asm/MethodVisitor.html .

There is no CheckAnnotationVisitorFsm at this time.
